Template: agentic-kali/accept-terms
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Accept Agentic Kali authorized-use terms?
 Agentic Kali is only for authorized security testing, defensive assessment,
 education, and lab research. You must have explicit permission for all targets.

Template: agentic-kali/azure-endpoint
Type: string
Description: Azure OpenAI endpoint
 Example: https://YOUR-RESOURCE.openai.azure.com

Template: agentic-kali/azure-key
Type: password
Description: Azure OpenAI API key
 Leave blank to configure later with agentic-kali config.

Template: agentic-kali/azure-deployment
Type: string
Description: Azure OpenAI deployment name
 The model deployment name configured in Azure OpenAI.

Template: agentic-kali/azure-api-version
Type: string
Default: 2025-04-01-preview
Description: Azure OpenAI API version

